00:38:25.890 --> 00:38:27.000
It never lines up.

00:38:27.000 --> 00:38:28.920
Or if it does line
up perfectly, how

00:38:28.920 --> 00:38:29.710
long does it last?

00:38:29.710 --> 00:38:31.420
It's transitory.

00:38:31.420 --> 00:38:35.000
So most the time, the world
doesn't line up perfectly.

00:38:35.000 --> 00:38:38.590
And so we really need to be
effective at dealing with a

00:38:38.590 --> 00:38:43.340
world that's constantly changing
and not perfect.

00:38:43.340 --> 00:38:46.770
So, no, the goal isn't to banish
stress or discomfort.

00:38:46.770 --> 00:38:51.090
The goal is OK, if discomfort
is here to stay, we got to

00:38:51.090 --> 00:38:52.470
manage it well.

00:38:52.470 --> 00:38:56.660
And if we manage it well, it
facilitates performance.

00:38:56.660 --> 00:39:00.540
It doesn't lead to
an apathy at all.

