00:39:15.610 --> 00:39:19.150
helpful effect on the
brain, on the body.

00:39:19.150 --> 00:39:22.410
One of the things that
meditation can do--

00:39:22.410 --> 00:39:25.940
mindful meditation is the one
I'm most familiar with--

00:39:25.940 --> 00:39:30.050
