cerebral brain.

00:39:32.940 --> 00:39:35.430
So it brings them into
better balance.

00:39:35.430 --> 00:39:36.390
The problem--

00:39:36.390 --> 00:39:39.140
what happens is that as we
become uncomfortable or

00:39:39.140 --> 00:39:43.840
experience trauma, it
destabilizes the brain.

00:39:43.840 --> 00:39:47.310
So that often this limbic
emotional brain is the one

00:39:47.310 --> 00:39:50.870
that has hold of the steering
wheel, and it's the one

00:39:50.870 --> 00:39:53.160
driving the car.

00:39:53.160 --> 00:39:58.990
But meditation, and the one I
believe a lot in is hypnosis,

00:39:58.990 --> 00:40:03.280
can bring both these parts
of the brain back

00:40:03.280 --> 00:40:06.170
into a balance state.

00:40:06.170 --> 00:40:08.430
But mindful meditation is
the one that has the

00:40:08.430 --> 00:40:10.550
most data on it.

